{"id": 2655, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得当代社交媒体上最稀缺的能力是什么？", "description": "一些“随着社交媒体的普及反而显得越来越少见”的能力。（题图来自：iStock ©️ Comomolas）", "record_count": 4646, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181203173218yUxDZaimEJgVnHvB.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-12-06T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 317696, "content": "露素颜，说真话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1536533}, {"id": 315137, "content": "发表意见前核实相关内容", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500770}, {"id": 315138, "content": "独立思考  表达能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441783}, {"id": 315139, "content": "你mark 生活，分享，阐述你的观点可以.  \n但麻烦你认真的也把别人的话 听完. 别断章取义，给别人套上标签.  讨厌- 很多人说 -大家都是这么做的.我就想问问-是应该忠于对与否的执念.还是 多数人的认同；不能代表我的认同. 不要以多数人认同的观念来 论证我的想法是错的. ", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524981}, {"id": 315141, "content": "好好写字，好好说话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428289}, {"id": 315142, "content": "独立思考的能力，容易被带方向", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522391}, {"id": 333063, "content": "思辨能力 客观性", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 315143, "content": "脑子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429979}, {"id": 316167, "content": "观点中立", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234107}, {"id": 315144, "content": "经过思考后的表达", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1468897}, {"id": 315400, "content": "交到知心朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1471964}, {"id": 315656, "content": "写超过140字的段落 并保持逻辑自洽", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527916}, {"id": 315145, "content": "这条信息看都没看完就分享给朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168304}, {"id": 315402, "content": "事件真假完整性客观评价 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525825}, {"id": 315147, "content": "面对面沟通的能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026473}, {"id": 316939, "content": "不跟风，不炒作。无杠精。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532602}, {"id": 315148, "content": "独立思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522844}, {"id": 315404, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271793}, {"id": 315149, "content": "文明用语、不说脏话，客观看待事件和别人的发言", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050868}, {"id": 315405, "content": "带着自己的脑子说话\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1520378}, {"id": 315150, "content": "客观。\n真正的客观。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437436}, {"id": 315662, "content": "客观事实\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527913}, {"id": 316942, "content": "说这么多 还是读书太少", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532644}, {"id": 315151, "content": "股票配资5~20倍，停牌可结算，穿仓不用赔，加:li2323239", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525025}, {"id": 315407, "content": "屏蔽那些流量明星的新闻", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524007}, {"id": 315152, "content": "现实中结交新朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064040}, {"id": 315664, "content": "语言简练，想法独立，能够取一个和内容相符的题目。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1487828}, {"id": 315153, "content": "先别看别人的评论", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386953}, {"id": 315154, "content": "对自己每个字负责。不乱用词语", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 444860}, {"id": 315156, "content": "静下心看完一本书的能力吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511966}, {"id": 315157, "content": "分清虚拟与现实，清楚自身定位", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360680}, {"id": 315413, "content": "康德所谓“一个成熟的人”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 989435}, {"id": 315158, "content": "不带节奏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1111488}, {"id": 315159, "content": "坚持自我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496756}, {"id": 315415, "content": "自主能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1520109}, {"id": 318487, "content": "带上脑子闭上嘴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538092}, {"id": 315160, "content": "保持客观的能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1487129}, {"id": 315416, "content": "生而为人，请你善良；谨言慎行，不耍嘴炮；独立思考，切莫跟风；反之别人给你的人设标签会是：渣渣！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1517664}, {"id": 315161, "content": "对一件事情独立思考的能力\n太多人跟着别人无脑走", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508992}, {"id": 315162, "content": "不要太偏激", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524400}, {"id": 315418, "content": "无数热点更迭滚动，怎么在其中甄选出理性的观点。在漫天节奏党的咆哮中，如何听到角落里面的智人说的人话。在非黑即白的暴力输出环境里如何从容的掏出我自岿然不动的防护罩，坚定的不被口水大军吓倒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525953}, {"id": 315163, "content": "真实性，有自己的判断力，而不是被带节奏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524352}, {"id": 315164, "content": "写出经过独立思考判断的内容，而不是无厘头盲目发言", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434421}, {"id": 315420, "content": "自媒体基本没脑子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525958}, {"id": 314397, "content": "完整阅读一篇不带动图和表情包的公众号文章", "image": null, "praise_count": 534, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 315421, "content": "缺乏真相，炒作和造谣居多，各种夸大事实，就为了流量", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525972}, {"id": 314398, "content": "写一段不用流行语、不带错别字、不乱用标点和成语的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 609, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 315422, "content": "缺少对事件的真实报道，标题党，浮夸，缺少独立客观的见解，更多的像吃快餐，看完发现并没有什么用，反而浪费了时间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962238}, {"id": 316446, "content": "普罗大众可能根本不关心内容是否真实，而是内容讲了什么事情，这个事情能否取悦自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678667}, {"id": 315423, "content": "追求真实", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525976}]}